# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Diagramforce — PRODUCTION (GitHub Pages) repo
#
# Ships ONLY the static app. Everything dev-only is filtered, so `git add -A`
# after copying from the dev folder stages just the app files. (Listed files may
# physically exist in the folder after a copy — git won't track them, so Pages
# never serves them.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Test suite + its tooling (the app itself is build-free & dependency-free)
tests/
scripts/
playwright.config.js
package.json
package-lock.json
node_modules/
test-results/
playwright-report/
playwright/.cache/
blob-report/

# CI lives on the private dev repo, not here. A copied workflow would run and
# fail (no test suite in this repo).
.github/

# Internal dev docs + assistant files — not public
Documentation/
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
diagramforce.mdx
examples/

# Dev-only debug pages
reset.html

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~